      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "The warming has already allowed the snowpack to settle a little. Due to the mild temperatures and solar radiation, the snowpack is rapidly losing its firmness. On the northern slopes, the kinetic metamorphism (cup crystals in the snow layer close to the ground!) continues to weaken the snowpack."
      },
